    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chromatography with paper strips or sheets as the adsorbent through which the solution flows by gravity or is sucked up by capillarity.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
